valued wave functions--

00:02:45.720 --> 00:02:48.360
wave functions would
be the same at phi,

00:02:48.360 --> 00:02:52.730
and at phi plus 2 pi,
which is the same point.

00:02:52.730 --> 00:02:57.380
You must choose m
to be an integer.

00:02:57.380 --> 00:03:00.020
For the l squared
operator we also

00:03:00.020 --> 00:03:03.770
explained that the
eigenvalue of this operator

00:03:03.770 --> 00:03:05.610
should be positive.

00:03:05.610 --> 00:03:08.870
That is achieved when
